55713/https://metacritic.com/movie/black-panther |archive-date=February 9, 2018  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A+}}<ref name=\"Marcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Avengers: Infinity War''\n| 85% (451 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avengers_infinity_war |title=Avengers: Infinity War (2018) |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]] |accessdate=2018-04-28 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427004733/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avengers_infinity_war |archive-date=April 27, 2018  }}</ref>\n| 68 (53 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://metacritic.com/movie/avengers-infinity-war |title=Avengers: Infinity War |website=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=April 25, 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117034655/https://metacritic.com/movie/avengers-infinity-war |archive-date=January 17, 2018  }}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A}}<ref name=\"Marcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Deadpool 2''\n| 84% (398 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deadpool_2 |title=Deadpool 2 (2018) |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]] |accessdate=May 15, 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424032015/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deadpool_2/ |archive-date=April 24, 2018  }}</ref>\n| 66 (51 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://metacritic.com/movie/deadpool-2|title=Deadpool 2|website=[[Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=May 16, 2018|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517125012/https://metacritic.com/movie/deadpool-2|archive-date=May 17, 2018}}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A}}<ref name=\"Marcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Ant-Man and the Wasp''\n| 88% (408 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ant_man_and_the_wasp |title=Ant-Man and the Wasp (2018) |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]] |accessdate=June 27, 2018}}</ref>\n| 70 (54 review